"format":false,"excerpt":"Sa\u2019d ibn Abi Waqqas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, this Quran has descended with sadness. If you recite it, then weep. If you cannot weep, then feign weeping. Recite in a melodious tone, for whoever does not use a pleasant voice is\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":29358,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/05\/13\/tilawat-al-quran-beautiful-voice\/","url_meta":{"origin":29360,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Tilawah: Reciting the Quran aloud in a pleasant voice","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 13, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cAllah does not listen to anything as he does to the beautiful voice of a prophet, reciting the Quran aloud pleasantly.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 7544, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 792 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32421,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/22\/parable-reciters-good-company\/","url_meta":{"origin":29360,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Company: Parable of Quran reciters, righteous friends","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 22, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe parable of the believer who recites the Quran is that of citron, whose fragrance and taste are pleasant. The parable of the believer who does not recite the Quran is that of a date, whose taste\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33256,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/08\/19\/abu-bakr-first-compile-quran\/","url_meta":{"origin":29360,"position":3},"title":"Ali on Quran: Abu Bakr first to compile Quran into one book","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 19, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"\u2018Abdu Khayr reported: Ali ibn Abi Talib, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cMay Allah have mercy on Abu Bakr. He was the first to compile the Quran between two covers.\u201d Source: Mus\u0323annaf Ibn Abi\u0304 Shaybah 30229 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Ibn Battal \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u062e\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32765,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/07\/12\/recite-quran-by-heart\/","url_meta":{"origin":29360,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Quran: Encouragement to memorize, not only read Quran","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 12, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu al-Qasim reported: Abu Umamah, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cRecite the Quran and do not be deceived by depending on the written copies. Verily, Allah will never punish a heart that has preserved the Quran.\u201d Source: Mus\u0323annaf Ibn Abi\u0304 Shaybah 34044 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Ibn\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":38882,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/02\/23\/abu-umamah-quran\/","url_meta":{"origin":29360,"position":5},"title":"Abu Umamah on Quran: Allah will not punish a heart preserving His Book","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 23, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Qasim reported: Abu Umamah, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cRecite the Quran and do not be mistaken about these connected pages, for Allah will not punish a heart that preserves the Quran.\u201d Source: Mus\u0323annaf Ibn Abi\u0304 Shaybah 34732 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Ibn Hajar \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0642\u064e\u0627\u0633\u0650\u0645 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/29360","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/po